external_knowledge:
The most viewed category is determined by summing up the views from all businesses within that category; 
A view is considered any instance of accessing the business listing with the 'view' access type;
An edit is considered any instance of accessing the business listing with the 'edit' access type.

sql:
SELECT b.name AS business_name
FROM businesses b
WHERE b.review_count > 10 AND b.verified = 1;

external_knowledge:
; Top-rated and frequently-reviewed businesses imply those with higher ratings and more reviews, respectively; 
; Currently open businesses are those with a 'status' of 'open'; 
; Accessed within the last 30 days means the business was viewed or interacted with on the platform within this timeframe;
; Foursquare and Yellow Pages are platforms or sources where businesses are listed.
